OL,3,CFormer Coop CEO alleges 'witch hunt'
OL,4,Cled to him being sacked
OL,6,FThe former CEO of the Channel Islands
OL,7,FCoop has taken his old employer to
OL,8,Fcourt for a personal injury civil
OL,9,Fclaim.
OL,11,FColin Macleod was in the top job
OL,12,Fbetween 2010 and 2020 and alleges four
OL,13,Fdirectors conspired to remove him,
OL,14,Fleading to him being signed off with
OL,15,Fstress before a subsequent sick leave
OL,16,Fperiod culminated in the termination
OL,17,Fof his contract.
OL,19,FHe had been at the Coop since he was
OL,20,F20 years old, working his way up from
OL,21,Fthe shop floor to the boardroom.
