OL,3,CFormer Coop CEO alleges 'witch hunt'
OL,4,Cled to him being sacked
OL,6,FMacleod described the events to
OL,7,FJersey's Royal Court as a "mercy
OL,8,Fkilling" and said there was a "witch
OL,9,Fhunt" to get him out.
OL,11,FHe alleged the company had "no respect
OL,12,Ffor duty of care" after he was blocked
OL,13,Ffrom his work email accounts without
OL,14,Fconsultation.
OL,16,FMacleod told the court there was "no
OL,17,Frespect or regard" for his health and
OL,18,Fdescribed it as "shutting off life
OL,19,Fsupport".
