OL,6,FHe added: "It was like cutting off an
OL,7,Fumbilical cord. I belonged to that
OL,8,Forganisation.
OL,10,F"The irony of the company's motto:
OL,11,F'Belonging is everything'."
OL,13,FAdvocate Jeremy Heywood, representing
OL,14,Fthe Channel Islands Coop, told the
OL,15,Fcourt during cross-examination that
OL,16,Fthe "decision was taken to allow you
OL,17,Fto focus on your recovery".
