OL,6,FMacleod, however, argued: "I am a sick
OL,7,Fman, making a desperate effort to find
OL,8,Fout what had happened.
OL,10,F"I didn't need pills or therapists,
OL,11,Fthe pill I needed was someone to sit
OL,12,Fdown and tell me what had happened, so
OL,13,FI could control my thoughts."
OL,15,FMacleod told the court: "I am here
OL,16,Ftoday receiving treatment, trying to
OL,17,Funderstand what actually happened, so
OL,18,FI can move on with my life.
