OL,6,F"The therapy I needed was to
OL,7,Funderstand what had happened, it's
OL,8,Ftaken me five years to limp to here
OL,9,F... and I'm still ostracised.
OL,11,F"This is the hardest thing I've ever
OL,12,Fhad to do. Litigation is very
OL,13,Fdifficult, the delays, the denials,
OL,14,Fthe insults, but a necessary journey
OL,15,Fto get better."
