OL,6,FThe Channel Islands Coop denies the
OL,7,Fclaims and said: "The Society is
OL,8,Fcommitted to upholding integrity,
OL,9,Ftransparency, and the highest ethical
OL,10,Fstandards. We approach any complaint
OL,11,Fraised against us with utmost
OL,12,Fseriousness. The Society does not
OL,13,Faccept the allegations made against it
OL,14,Fby Mr Macleod.
OL,16,F"While we understand the public
OL,17,Finterest in this matter, the matter is
OL,18,Fnow in the hands of the Court for
OL,19,Fresolution. We must respect the legal
OL,20,Fprocess. As such, we will not make any
OL,21,Ffurther comment at this time."
